QuestData.Title: Blackfathom Deeps
QuestData.Description: There's a task to be done that you're perfect for, $c. We need to secure the area around Blackfathom Deeps to help with the Alliance that are threatening Zoram'gar Outpost west of here.$B$BGo to Blackfathom Deeps, north of Zoram'gar Outpost, and speak with Je'neu of the Earthen Ring. He will have plenty for you to do.
